</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \langle U_{g}[e],[e]\rangle _{f}=\int _{\widehat {G}}\xi (g)\,d\mu (\xi ).}">
